name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Food Hygiene Ratings for Just Eat

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Displays the food hygiene ratings of restaurants prominently on area searches.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds hygiene ratings from the Food Standards Agency into the restaurant lists of the Just Eat website, so you can make a more informed choice when ordering.

This extension is not provided by Just Eat or the Food Standards Agency in any way.
